dct_title_s: Rußland  (Kaukasus) 1:200 000 / Generalstab des Heeres Abteilung für Kriegskarten- und VermessungswesenHerausgestellt im Auftrag Gen St d H Abt f Kr Kart u Verm Wes (II).
dct_description_sm: Gauß-Krüger grid. Relief shown by contours, shading, hachures and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines on some maps. Include index to sheet. Follows IMW grid system. Our holdings contents the following quadrangles. Portions of: L-37 Rostow, L-38 Pjatigorsk, K-37 Batum, K-38 Tiflis, K-39 Baku. Includes index to boundaries and list of abbreviations.
dct_creator_sm: Germany. Heer. Abteilung für Kriegskarten- und Vermessungswesen
dct_publisher_sm: Berlin : Herausgestellt im Auftrag Gen St d H Abt f Kr Kart u Verm Wes (II), 1941-42.
dct_spatial_sm: Russia. Russian Empire. Soviet Union. Former Soviet Republics
